features: 【Wide Compatibility】This cell phone stand is compatible with all 4-8 inches smartphones in phone cases, like iPhone 13 12 mini 11 Pro XS Max XR X 8 7 6 6S Plus, Galaxy S21 Ultra, S20, S10, S9, S9 Plus, A71, A51, A11, Edge, Note 20 ultra, LG, Sony, Moto, LG, Google Pixel, Nexus etc.

【Stable and Anti-scratch】The iPhone stand is made of high-quality aluminum alloy with a nice finish. Stable and easy to watch Youtube or FaceTime. Besides, rubber non-slip pads protect the surface of your phone case and desk from scratches.

【Make Your Life Easier】Using this desktop phone holder at home to prop up your phone, you can better view recipes while cooking. It's also great for on your nightstand, so no more fumbling around in the morning to shut off the alarm.

【Suitable Viewing Angle】The phone cradle for desk provides you with a comfortable viewing angle. Put it on your office desk, and you can see at a glace incoming notifications and calls when the phone is in silent mode.

【Thoughtful Detail Design】 A large hole in the back allows a charging cable to bend gracefully away. And the outer edge of this hole is beveled so that it will not cut into your cord — a perfect dock for your phone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish and Functional Desk Companion
reviews.reviewText: The Lamicall Cell Phone Stand has been an absolute game-changer for my office desk setup. This versatile and sleek phone stand not only keeps my phone at a perfect viewing angle but also adds a touch of style to my workspace.One of the standout features of this phone stand is its sturdy construction. The premium-quality materials and solid base ensure that my phone stays securely in place, providing a reliable and stable cradle for my device.The adjustable design allows me to find the ideal viewing angle, whether I'm watching videos, reading articles, or participating in video calls. It eliminates the strain on my neck and hands by keeping my phone at eye level, promoting a comfortable and ergonomic posture.The phone stand's black color complements my office decor beautifully, adding a touch of sophistication without being too flashy or distracting.I appreciate the thoughtful design, which includes a space at the bottom of the stand to route charging cables neatly. It helps keep my desk tidy and clutter-free.The Lamicall brand's commitment to quality is evident in this phone stand's performance and durability. It has withstood daily use and still looks as good as new.The rubberized pads on the stand's base and cradle protect my phone from scratches and ensure a secure grip without leaving any marks.The phone stand's compact and lightweight design makes it portable, allowing me to use it on my desk, kitchen counter, or even while traveling.In conclusion, the Lamicall Cell Phone Stand is the perfect desk companion for anyone seeking a stylish and functional solution to hold their phone. Its adjustable design, sturdy construction, and cable management feature make it an ideal addition to any office setup. If you're looking for a reliable and versatile phone stand that enhances your phone usage experience, I highly recommend the Lamicall Cell Phone Stand. Embrace the convenience and style it brings to your workspace, and enjoy a comfortable and enjoyable phone experience like never before!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love its multi-use capability!
reviews.reviewText: I really like this little stand and, after seeing it, my son also bought one. I use it primarily with my phone, but also found that it holds my Nintendo Switch perfectly when using the controllers separately. Great for hands-free viewing such as video calls. Phone can be put on the stand in upright or sideways position. It has a small footprint and is designed for ease during charging. The hole in the back helps to corral the cord, and the design allows ample space for plugging into the bottom of the phone. All in all, a great little stand at a great price.

reviews.reviewTitle: Extremely well designed and super stable and sturdy!!!
reviews.reviewText: Definitely the best smartphone stand I have bought till date on Amazon. Bought it after I had already purchased a similar product from the same seller for my tablet. I bought it in a lightning deal with a small discount, but even without the discount it would have been a great deal for the price. The stand itself is very well designed, the metallic body is light, compact and sturdy. It looks great on my home office desk and I plan to get atleast a couple more for my work. The extra pads that the manufacturer sent with the package are a plus. But with a few days of heavy use, I can already confirm that there is no slippage and it takes the weight of my iPhone 7 really well. I have tried it with a few other smartphone models and it shows the same stability with all of them. The only design enhancement, albeit a really small one, that I would suggest for a future model would be to allow more room on either side of the arm that holds the phone so that the phone can be placed on it with the headphones in the socket. It is not an inconvenience though, the phone just has to sit a little bit to the left in that case. All in all, I am extremely pleased and would highly recommend.
Great Price, holds phone vertical or horizontal, perfect, nothing much can go wrong
